  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d91\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0dc3.\u0da2.\u0db6 \u0dbd\u0ddc\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc3 \u0d9c\u0dc4\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A SJB boss who was about to join the government backs down",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that a person who went by the name of Samagi Jana Balavega, who was the subject of a lot of talk recently about joining the government, is now making efforts to join the government.",
        "It has been learned from political sources that this has happened because the post of Finance Minister was not received.",
        "The government has decided to give him the position of Policy Planning Minister. But the sources also state that he has not agreed to it.",
        "Meanwhile, government sources said that the appointment of other ministers of the government's cabinet will be done after the presentation of the interim budget next week.",
        "It is learned that it has been delayed in order to prevent the matter from being criticized during the budget debates.",
        "Meanwhile, while appointing ministers, the government has planned to appoint state ministers first."
      ],
